{"tid":501730,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"(Family Man) 罕有孖秦舒培情侶裝放閃 陳冠希：TWINSIES","createTime":"2017-12-17T06:56:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-18T16:46:04.000Z","uid":156068,"like":2,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"6e5b55494063a9fca870f6d40e47266d88dabdb6","tid":501730,"uid":156068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T06:56:30.000Z","msg":"37歲嘅陳冠希（Edison）喺去年被《蘋果》踢爆撻着內地超模秦舒培，之後仲為女友喺社交平台鬧爆林志玲，似乎都仲係咁大火氣（相關新聞: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2j6OSkV\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2j6OSkV&d=CbnD%2Fe2fgdhdmOHQVZijsdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=a5e1fd0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2j6OSkV</a> ）。<br />\n<br />\n不過喺今年秦舒培為Edison誕下囡囡Alaia，而Edison亦都好似好快進入咗「family man」呢個mode，佢不時喺IG post女友秦舒培同囡囡嘅相，非常之咁幸福咁噃。而今日Edison仲罕有放閃o添！佢post咗張同女友黐到實嘅合照，佢哋仲着埋情侶裝，而Edison就留言：「TWINSIES」，睇下佢哋笑得幾sweet就知幾幸福啦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/17/145618_fd453e2af59da9a1a2ae4ca3a356631a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F17%2F145618_fd453e2af59da9a1a2ae4ca3a356631a.jpg&h=41486cff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/17/145619_577d4203a5bf1c8a1e58cf91c08125e3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F17%2F145619_577d4203a5bf1c8a1e58cf91c08125e3.jpg&h=efa245dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/17/145619_abd90aa02bcea3ee88eaed0700e75721.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F17%2F145619_abd90aa02bcea3ee88eaed0700e75721.jpg&h=bf581013&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4c777777cc87ad3143fd9ece9d487f88a2041e24","tid":501730,"uid":13724,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T07:07:06.000Z","msg":"第一張相咁似男人嘅"},{"pid":"518272ad8d6b625abb28131da9e86a5bf5cfa1c2","tid":50173